snippet.title: 'Don't get brazen with me': Kyle Rittenhouse judge slams prosecutor
snippet.description:
Outside the presence of the jury, Kyle Rittenhouse trial Judge Bruce Schroeder loudly scolded prosecutor Thomas Binger in a dramatic exchange in court.
